WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: TDEbmRyCtxg

NOTE Language: en

00:00:02.220 --> 00:00:07.590
… that the source of joy is within your
Self.

00:00:07.590 --> 00:00:15.160
Unless and until you seek your Self you cannot
seek God.

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:22.029
They have all talked about the second birth.

00:00:22.029 --> 00:00:36.960
What we call the baptism is also the same
where you have to be born again.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:41.690
Is not just a formal one that is done by unauthorized
people.

00:00:41.690 --> 00:00:59.830
Even the word “Musalman”, Mohammed Sahib
has again and again talked of a rebirth.

00:00:59.830 --> 00:01:06.190
You have to find your Self.

00:01:06.190 --> 00:01:07.190
How do we find our Selves is the problem.

00:01:07.190 --> 00:01:08.190
Is there something like “Self”?

00:01:08.190 --> 00:01:21.070
Is there really something like “God” or
it’s all a myth?

00:01:21.070 --> 00:01:36.120
Is there any fact in following the religious
holy life that you get your salvation?

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:43.820
So far, we have had no proof of it.

00:01:43.820 --> 00:01:50.850
Naturally, in this scientific world today
you have to give the proof of everything to

00:01:50.850 --> 00:01:55.720
convince people so that they seek them Selves.

00:01:55.720 --> 00:02:08.970
But the science tells us that we were evolved
from a little amoeba to a human being.

00:02:08.970 --> 00:02:10.290
Why?

00:02:10.290 --> 00:02:13.310
Why God took so much trouble?

00:02:13.310 --> 00:02:16.220
If you don’t believe in God you can say
nature.

00:02:16.220 --> 00:02:24.470
Why nature worked so hard to create a human
being out of a small little amoeba?

00:02:24.470 --> 00:02:32.550
Supposing we assemble some screws, and we
try to work out something, a passer-by would

00:02:32.550 --> 00:02:33.550
ask, “Why?

00:02:33.550 --> 00:02:37.020
What are you going to make out of this instrument?

00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:45.060
What are you doing?”

00:02:45.060 --> 00:02:55.840
There must be some reason why we have become
human beings after so much of evolution.

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:59.960
But science doesn’t think of “why."

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:04.090
It just tells you, “This is."

00:03:04.090 --> 00:03:08.240
And whatever is not there, it says, “We
can’t explain."

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:19.879
The instrument, whatever it is, supposing
has to work on electrical energy or on any

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:29.560
energy whatsoever will come into force or
will start working out when it is connected

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.099
to the mains.

00:03:31.099 --> 00:03:43.510
Otherwise it is still in the making process
or you can say it is in transition.

00:03:43.510 --> 00:03:48.330
Human being as such is in transition.

00:03:48.330 --> 00:03:54.390
It has not found its own meaning.

00:03:54.390 --> 00:04:02.650
He does not know why he exists, what is the
purpose of his life.

00:04:02.650 --> 00:04:07.319
It’s a meaningless life.

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:10.350
So, you have to be connected to the mains.

00:04:10.350 --> 00:04:18.061
That’s what everybody has been saying that
you have to be reborn, you have to become

00:04:18.061 --> 00:04:19.220
that.

00:04:19.220 --> 00:04:25.650
Now, those who talked of this were born on
the tenth storey.

00:04:25.650 --> 00:04:31.300
The rest of them are on this earth.

00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:38.820
When they talked it all went over their heads.

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:43.330
You have to at least reach the first or second
storey to understand that there is something

00:04:43.330 --> 00:04:46.560
beyond this human consciousness, this human
awareness.

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:50.330
There’s something more to this awareness.

00:04:50.330 --> 00:04:53.730
There’s a more opening.

00:04:53.730 --> 00:05:02.640
There’s a greater dimension which one has
to achieve to understand your own meaning.

00:05:02.640 --> 00:05:09.910
About Kundalini all the scriptures, I must
say, have described, all the scriptures without

00:05:09.910 --> 00:05:10.910
exception.

00:05:10.910 --> 00:05:28.030
Of course, in India there has been a very
deep meditation tendency thousands of years

00:05:28.030 --> 00:05:43.480
back and some of the seers long time back
found out about Kundalini, and even in [Dhirenja

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:44.480
Sangita?]

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:45.480
Kundalini is described.

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:47.670
That’s as old, I should say, about Vedas.

00:05:47.670 --> 00:05:52.280
We cannot say the origin of these books.

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:54.680
Kundalini has been described in them.

00:05:54.680 --> 00:06:00.070
Kundalini has been again and again described
and also abused and misused and misrepresented.

00:06:00.070 --> 00:06:06.330
All sorts of things have been done about Kundalini.

00:06:06.330 --> 00:06:19.440
In the Bible Kundalini has been described
in such a manner that it is not called as

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:25.830
Kundalini, but they call it as “Tree of
Fire,” “Tongues of Flames."

00:06:25.830 --> 00:06:32.690
Many such adjectives, descriptions are used,
but they have not used the word Kundalini

00:06:32.690 --> 00:06:38.400
itself because it is not written in Sanskrit
language.

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:45.639
So, there must be some mechanism within us
by which we are reborn, no doubt.

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:47.960
There has to be some mechanism.

00:06:47.960 --> 00:06:58.759
If I’m speaking through this mike to you,
there must be some mechanism which is doing

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:02.000
the job.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:10.370
In every seed there is a premule, the mechanism
which germinates and creates a big tree out

00:07:10.370 --> 00:07:11.440
of it.

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:21.700
In the same way we have a mechanism placed
within us.

00:07:21.700 --> 00:07:25.949
But this is a very subtle thing while human
beings are absolutely gross.

00:07:25.949 --> 00:07:35.460
In this Kali Yuga, modern times, they are
even worse, extremely gross and they cannot

00:07:35.460 --> 00:07:39.830
think of something subtle.

00:07:39.830 --> 00:07:45.350
If I tell you there is an energy which thinks,
organizes, loves, you cannot think of such

00:07:45.350 --> 00:07:46.350
an energy.

00:07:46.350 --> 00:07:48.229
But how do we organize?

00:07:48.229 --> 00:07:49.520
How do we think?

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:50.520
How do we love?

00:07:50.520 --> 00:07:52.930
From where do we get that energy?

00:07:52.930 --> 00:07:54.949
Why shouldn’t we think about it?

00:07:54.949 --> 00:08:02.530
But as I said that modern man doesn’t think
of “how,” he takes it for granted.

00:08:02.530 --> 00:08:09.410
So, today I want to tell you about this mechanism
that exists within you.

00:08:09.410 --> 00:08:14.210
It should not be just a mental feat with you.

00:08:14.210 --> 00:08:15.210
No!

00:08:15.210 --> 00:08:22.000
It should not be the so-called knowledge of
Kundalini from outside but it’s a happening

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:29.650
where the Kundalini rises and you get that
whatever is promised in all the scriptures.

00:08:29.650 --> 00:08:40.560
Today the time has come to prove the existence
of the Divine Power of God all around us.

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:43.490
We have been going and praying to God.

00:08:43.490 --> 00:08:45.679
Does He listen to us?

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:46.679
Are we connected to Him?

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:55.199
We do namaz, we spread our hands towards God
Almighty, are we connected with Him or we

00:08:55.199 --> 00:08:58.339
are just doing a mechanical thing?

00:08:58.339 --> 00:09:00.839
Even so many people are doing Hatha Yoga.

00:09:00.839 --> 00:09:05.759
They think they are doing it in the name of
God.

00:09:05.759 --> 00:09:08.449
Is it a correct method?

00:09:08.449 --> 00:09:11.689
Can we do anything about it?

00:09:11.689 --> 00:09:20.120
If it is a living process, if it is an evolutionary
process, we must think we have done nothing

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:22.240
for our own evolution so far.

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:31.600
From amoeba to this stage we have come without
doing anything about it.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:39.759
We have taken our human life for granted.

00:09:39.759 --> 00:09:42.489
So what can we do about it?

00:09:42.489 --> 00:09:50.730
If it is a living process, it has to be spontaneous,
it has to work by itself, like a seed which

00:09:50.730 --> 00:09:54.800
is planted germinates by itself.

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:58.480
At the most a gardener can pour little water.

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:08.569
I can pour the water of My love on your seed
– at the most but the seed has to germinate

00:10:08.569 --> 00:10:10.410
by itself spontaneously.

00:10:10.410 --> 00:10:12.529
It is a living process and not the mechanical
process.

00:10:12.529 --> 00:10:18.749
Perhaps we never realize what is a living
process because we take it for granted.

00:10:18.749 --> 00:10:24.860
You see so many flowers turning into fruits
but we never think how it happens.

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:27.499
We have no idea of spontaneity.

00:10:27.499 --> 00:10:31.319
We think by doing something we are being spontaneous.

00:10:31.319 --> 00:10:40.350
So one has to be effortless because Kundalini
is born with you.

00:10:40.350 --> 00:10:43.360
‘Sahaja’: ‘born with you’.

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.610
‘Saha’ means ‘with’.

00:10:45.610 --> 00:10:47.869
Born with you.

00:10:47.869 --> 00:10:50.129
‘Ja’ means ‘born’.

00:10:50.129 --> 00:11:03.959
So awakening is a happening which happens
to you when somebody who is awakened, like

00:11:03.959 --> 00:11:15.949
an enlightened light or a candle, comes near
other lights which are not yet enlightened

00:11:15.949 --> 00:11:18.990
and enlightens it spontaneously.

00:11:18.990 --> 00:11:22.690
Now you cannot argue it out, you cannot.

00:11:22.690 --> 00:11:32.360
You cannot rationalize it because rationality
is a limited thing.

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:36.360
You have to go to something that is unlimited.

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:39.420
How can you do it with a limited mind?

00:11:39.420 --> 00:11:44.709
This is beyond mind you have to rise.

00:11:44.709 --> 00:11:50.959
If you argue it out, you are going to be away
from it.

00:11:50.959 --> 00:12:02.049
But in science we have found out many things
which indicate, which actually prepares the

00:12:02.049 --> 00:12:11.790
stage for Sahaja Yoga, which prepares us to
know that there’s something beyond.

00:12:11.790 --> 00:12:23.529
We have accepted in the medical science that
we have autonomous nervous system which works

00:12:23.529 --> 00:12:24.699
by itself.

00:12:24.699 --> 00:12:28.790
We call it ‘auto’: souayam [somatic-?],
chyme.

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:31.120
Who is this “auto”?

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:33.649
Who is this “one”?

00:12:33.649 --> 00:12:40.379
The one who beats your heart, the one who
digests your food?

00:12:40.379 --> 00:12:48.059
When we said that it is done by a system,
you just give it a name.

00:12:48.059 --> 00:12:49.989
But how do you explain?

00:12:49.989 --> 00:12:52.369
You cannot do it.

00:12:52.369 --> 00:12:58.939
You may be able to increase the rate of your
heart beat but you cannot decrease it.

00:12:58.939 --> 00:13:02.410
It happens spontaneously, automatically.

00:13:02.410 --> 00:13:05.879
How does it happen?

00:13:05.879 --> 00:13:10.089
By giving it a name you do not explain.

00:13:10.089 --> 00:13:22.439
In psychology people have found out that there
is something like a universal Unconscious.

00:13:22.439 --> 00:13:30.519
There is that “sarvavyapi achetan” [all-pervasive
action] which gives symbolic suggestions in

00:13:30.519 --> 00:13:34.009
the dreams which are universally the same.

00:13:34.009 --> 00:13:38.019
They’ve accepted this.

00:13:38.019 --> 00:13:47.600
They have proved it by experiments that there
is a universal unconscious, so many of them.

00:13:47.600 --> 00:13:55.259
I shouldn’t say all of them because, you
see, after all there will be always a controversy

00:13:55.259 --> 00:13:58.999
till you reach the truth.

00:13:58.999 --> 00:14:02.120
Human mind must have something to eat.

00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:09.800
But they have, they talk of it.

00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:19.269
Scientists cannot explain many things.

00:14:19.269 --> 00:14:23.329
There is another thing which science cannot
explain is why certain things act differently

00:14:23.329 --> 00:14:24.889
in a human body.

00:14:24.889 --> 00:14:31.290
For example there are two chemicals known
as adrenaline and acetylcholine.

00:14:31.290 --> 00:14:34.129
They have certain chemical reaction.

00:14:34.129 --> 00:14:37.720
But in the body they react differently.

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:44.199
They cannot explain, they just say the mood
of action of these chemicals in the human

00:14:44.199 --> 00:14:47.769
body cannot be explained.

00:14:47.769 --> 00:14:50.480
Finished.

00:14:50.480 --> 00:14:59.949
In the human body or in any body as such whichever
is living, any foreign matter is thrown out.

00:14:59.949 --> 00:15:11.839
But when a mother conceives a child in the
womb it is not thrown out, but it is nurtured

00:15:11.839 --> 00:15:13.350
and looked after.

00:15:13.350 --> 00:15:14.869
Who does that?

00:15:14.869 --> 00:15:21.509
Who understands that this is not a foreign
matter, but is a future child?

00:15:21.509 --> 00:15:28.649
Is there somebody thinking inside your uterus
or something that is controlling, who takes

00:15:28.649 --> 00:15:30.169
the decision?

00:15:30.169 --> 00:15:40.459
There must be someone or for [you], at least
minimum of a human level who thinks for you?

00:15:40.459 --> 00:15:53.519
So already there are questions for scientists
to ask and they all can be answered.

00:15:53.519 --> 00:16:07.490
Because the knowledge of science is analytical,
is in different corners, it gives you part-knowledge.

00:16:07.490 --> 00:16:15.920
Now Kundalini can be seen, you can see it.

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:18.089
The pulsation of the Kundalini you can see
at least.

00:16:18.089 --> 00:16:19.089
Many doctors have seen it now.

00:16:19.089 --> 00:16:21.449
In Delhi of course we don’t have any doctors
so far.

00:16:21.449 --> 00:16:23.749
I don’t know if among you there are any
doctors.

00:16:23.749 --> 00:16:29.339
But you can see with your own eyes the pulsation
of the Kundalini very clearly.

00:16:29.339 --> 00:16:38.149
If you have a stethoscope you can even feel
it, the rising of the anahata, means the throbbing.

00:16:38.149 --> 00:16:42.019
It can be done.

00:16:42.019 --> 00:16:55.689
But how long are we going to sit asking for
proof of a Kundalini?

00:16:55.689 --> 00:16:57.720
Let us now see.

00:16:57.720 --> 00:17:05.010
As I told you this morning you must accept
this as the hypothesis.

00:17:05.010 --> 00:17:11.429
Modern times are the worst times for one reason
that you have to explain everything which

00:17:11.429 --> 00:17:16.339
is a very simple thing as far as religion
is concerned.

00:17:16.339 --> 00:17:22.970
As far as other things are concerned you don’t
have to explain, people just accept.

00:17:22.970 --> 00:17:28.179
For example, if you have to put on this light
I have to just tell you that you go and switch

00:17:28.179 --> 00:17:29.179
on.

00:17:29.179 --> 00:17:32.830
That’s all, nobody argues.

00:17:32.830 --> 00:17:35.870
But today in the morning I told somebody to
put his hands towards Me like this, he started

00:17:35.870 --> 00:17:37.000
arguing on this point only, “Why should
I do it?”

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:39.100
Now I said, “I have to tell you the whole
thing, why it is to be done?”

00:17:39.100 --> 00:17:45.269
Is a simple gesture he could not do.

00:17:45.269 --> 00:17:51.200
And he has come here for the Kundalini rising,
you know, with all the rights on Me.

00:17:51.200 --> 00:17:53.510
You can’t even put your hands towards Me?

00:17:53.510 --> 00:17:58.660
Arguments have brought you nowhere.

00:17:58.660 --> 00:18:01.750
You must understand.

00:18:01.750 --> 00:18:06.450
This talking “bla, bla” has led you nowhere.

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:08.259
What have you achieved in that?

00:18:08.259 --> 00:18:12.389
You think you have done this job, built this
building you’ve done.

00:18:12.389 --> 00:18:16.179
It’s all dead, all dead things, dead converted
into another dead.

00:18:16.179 --> 00:18:22.760
What living work have you done so far?

00:18:22.760 --> 00:18:27.759
What have you done so far that you can call
as living?

00:18:27.759 --> 00:18:38.980
You cannot do even a seed sprout!

00:18:38.980 --> 00:18:46.100
The One who does millions and millions of
such things, billions and billions of these

00:18:46.100 --> 00:18:55.390
seeds sprouted, when we have to know Him,
at least let us have the humility to know

00:18:55.390 --> 00:19:03.330
that through your rationality and so-called
intellect you are not going to know Him.

00:19:03.330 --> 00:19:06.700
A little drop wants to know the whole of the
ocean!

00:19:06.700 --> 00:19:13.320
How can you explain to an ant the human civilization
and the human problems, and how can you explain

00:19:13.320 --> 00:19:23.159
to a human being the working of the subtle,
divine forces.

00:19:23.159 --> 00:19:27.210
God has been challenged by man.

00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:30.970
See the greatness!

00:19:30.970 --> 00:19:46.920
That’s why in all the scriptures it is written,
“Humble down yourself in your heart."

00:19:46.920 --> 00:19:52.480
That doesn’t mean that you give up your
intellect, doesn’t mean at all, but you

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:55.000
must have the balance of your heart also.

00:19:55.000 --> 00:20:08.470
So, with all these apologetic words and introduction,
I am now telling you about the Kundalini,

00:20:08.470 --> 00:20:12.929
where It exists, because now don’t start
from the very beginning doubting.

00:20:12.929 --> 00:20:16.539
Please keep your mind open.

00:20:16.539 --> 00:20:22.250
Later on when you get your realization through
Sahaja Yoga, when you practice it … Now

00:20:22.250 --> 00:20:26.029
we have many here who have got it.

00:20:26.029 --> 00:20:31.360
And they have seen the working of the Kundalini
and have confirmed what I’ve been saying

00:20:31.360 --> 00:20:32.360
about it.

00:20:32.360 --> 00:20:33.600
But to you it will be quite shocking.

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:45.630
I know it will be because you cannot believe
that such a thing can be inside us.

00:20:45.630 --> 00:20:51.669
Of course the mechanism has been simplified
because this is just a, I should say, a primary

00:20:51.669 --> 00:20:53.820
class, the first standard.

00:20:53.820 --> 00:20:59.460
So, it has not been that complicated as it
is.

00:20:59.460 --> 00:21:03.080
I’ll try to make it simpler and simpler.

00:21:03.080 --> 00:21:08.200
But you must know that it is a subtle thing
which you have not seen yourself, you’ve

00:21:08.200 --> 00:21:11.220
not felt it, you’ve not known it so far.

00:21:11.220 --> 00:21:22.880
It’s something out of the blue for you and
in this so called scientifically enlightened

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:31.279
world it may sound quite foolish to you that
I’m saying these things.

00:21:31.279 --> 00:21:34.510
But it is like this.

00:21:34.510 --> 00:21:35.909
Do not be fanatic about things.

00:21:35.909 --> 00:21:40.399
Even there are scientists who are real fanatics.

00:21:40.399 --> 00:21:50.600
Science is another obsession which has really
killed their foresight.

00:21:50.600 --> 00:21:53.340
Can you see from here?

00:21:53.340 --> 00:21:56.020
Now, this is the picture.

00:21:56.020 --> 00:22:00.809
As they say man is made in the image of God.

00:22:00.809 --> 00:22:07.110
We can say now, let us see, ‘Liver’s Tone’
means ‘the Object of which you are the reflection’.

00:22:07.110 --> 00:22:18.580
So we’ll start from the top.

00:22:18.580 --> 00:22:32.419
When the child is in the womb of the mother,
the energy which you do not know, the energy

00:22:32.419 --> 00:22:42.789
that is all pervading called as Chaitanya,
is the divine power of love of God which is

00:22:42.789 --> 00:22:43.789
all around us.

00:22:43.789 --> 00:22:47.490
This sounds quite poetic only to people; [for]
many people is just a poetry.

00:22:47.490 --> 00:22:49.320
But it is not, it’s a fact.

00:22:49.320 --> 00:22:54.000
Because we have never tried this power before,
we only know the power of hatred.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:23:04.760
So this power of divine love of God which
is all pervading, which is all around us,

00:23:04.760 --> 00:23:06.740
descends within us.

00:23:06.740 --> 00:23:18.261
Yes, it does in the human beings also, when
the child is in the womb of the mother.

00:23:18.261 --> 00:23:29.880
The brain of the man is evolved in such a
manner that it gets a shape of a prism, of

00:23:29.880 --> 00:23:39.240
a prism which has got three sides and a base.

00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:55.159
When this energy enters into the brain, then
it passes into all the surfaces of the brain,

00:23:55.159 --> 00:24:02.549
and some passes through the center on top
here.

00:24:02.549 --> 00:24:15.360
