They are human beings.

00:46:40.069 --> 00:46:47.060
Otherwise they are pischachas or rakshasas
or devils or satanic or they are sub-human.

00:46:47.060 --> 00:46:53.800
To be a human being minimum of minimum you
must have those ten qualities, ten dharmas

00:46:53.800 --> 00:46:54.800
within yourself.

00:46:54.800 --> 00:46:59.140
If you do not have, you are not a human being.

00:46:59.140 --> 00:47:00.300
You become satanic.

00:47:00.300 --> 00:47:01.900
You become sub-human.

00:47:01.900 --> 00:47:06.339
Your awareness goes down, it’s lowered.

00:47:06.339 --> 00:47:11.220
These are above the ten commandments I should
say, above because there are certain things

00:47:11.220 --> 00:47:15.079
which are not mentioned in them clearly, in
the Bible.

00:47:15.079 --> 00:47:23.630
These are the ten basic qualities in a human
being one should have, and if you do not have

00:47:23.630 --> 00:47:24.890
then there are problems.

00:47:24.890 --> 00:47:29.920
For example, we should not shock people – means
drinking.

00:47:29.920 --> 00:47:34.359
People say, “What’s wrong in drinking,
Mataji?”

00:47:34.359 --> 00:47:38.799
Simple thing, it goes against your awareness.

00:47:38.799 --> 00:47:43.859
See these drinks and all these alcohols they
are not created for drinking at all.

00:47:43.859 --> 00:47:47.779
They were created by God no doubt, but for
polishing.

00:47:47.779 --> 00:47:51.359
You see if you want to polish a diamond, you
have to use gin.

00:47:51.359 --> 00:47:54.130
Gin is not meant for drinking, for human consumption.

00:47:54.130 --> 00:47:55.250
It is not meant.

00:47:55.250 --> 00:48:00.839
This is human brain, you know, is such a wonderful
thing that it is using gin for their stomach

00:48:00.839 --> 00:48:02.589
which spoils their liver, gives them cancer.

00:48:02.589 --> 00:48:10.240
And you blame God for all these calamities
of the world.

00:48:10.240 --> 00:48:16.040
Smoking, now of course, many are saying smoking
causes cancer.

00:48:16.040 --> 00:48:17.700
Thank God.

00:48:17.700 --> 00:48:20.220
What is tobacco meant for?

