Is for insecticide, it’s an insecticide.

00:48:22.869 --> 00:48:26.369
I’m telling the truth.

00:48:26.369 --> 00:48:34.109
But ‘you’ use it for intoxication or what
you call, I don’t know.

00:48:34.109 --> 00:48:45.430
Now when all the gurus, even Moses, they told
about this.

00:48:45.430 --> 00:48:47.390
All the gurus have told.

