Incarnations have not but gurus have.

00:48:49.890 --> 00:48:51.079
I mean the real ones.

00:48:51.079 --> 00:48:53.940
I’m not saying these fake ones that are
these days, modern days are just making a

00:48:53.940 --> 00:48:56.880
business proposition of everything.

00:48:56.880 --> 00:49:05.859
I’m not talking about them but the real
ones, who are all born in this void – the

00:49:05.859 --> 00:49:10.520
void described by the Zen system of religion
– all the ten gurus.

00:49:10.520 --> 00:49:24.400
We can say the same there again the ten gurus
are incarnated, they tell us about the dharma.

00:49:24.400 --> 00:49:36.089
The center Nabhi Chakra is governed by the
deity called as Vishnu and His power is Lakshmi.

00:49:36.089 --> 00:49:46.660
Now, if your Nabhi Chakra is caught whatever
you may try you cannot get the blessings of

00:49:46.660 --> 00:49:47.780
Lakshmi.

00:49:47.780 --> 00:49:48.910
You cannot get.

00:49:48.910 --> 00:49:53.690
And even if you have lakshmi it will disappear.

00:49:53.690 --> 00:50:00.640
It’s a fact which can be proved.

00:50:00.640 --> 00:50:09.540
This Nabhi Chakra is controlled by a deity,
Vishnu, which is the sustaining aspect of

00:50:09.540 --> 00:50:10.910
God.

00:50:10.910 --> 00:50:18.980
Vishnu gives the different dharmas to us.

00:50:18.980 --> 00:50:24.240
That’s how He has evolved us from amoeba
to human beings.

00:50:24.240 --> 00:50:29.720
He Himself has incarnated as a leader many
a times.

00:50:29.720 --> 00:50:38.390
We call it Dashavatara and He has led us through
these incarnations.

00:50:38.390 --> 00:50:49.400
And His power is Lakshmi, is the Goddess of
welfare they say, or you can call it is wealth.

00:50:49.400 --> 00:50:50.400
It is not.

00:50:50.400 --> 00:50:53.140
It’s a very subtle thing, very subtle.

00:50:53.140 --> 00:51:03.109
That’s a symbol one should understand because
is concerned with us.

00:51:03.109 --> 00:51:11.770
Lakshmi has got a womanly figure, a mother’s
figure.

00:51:11.770 --> 00:51:14.849
She doesn’t have an actresses figure, you
see.

00:51:14.849 --> 00:51:20.810
They show of actresses and this beauty what
you call ‘beauty contests’, are not good

00:51:20.810 --> 00:51:22.470
vibrations at all.

00:51:22.470 --> 00:51:23.970
They do not emit any vibrations.

00:51:23.970 --> 00:51:30.190
On the contrary they emit very dirty vibrations,
I must say, very vulgar, very filthy.

00:51:30.190 --> 00:51:32.230
Lakshmi is a mother.

00:51:32.230 --> 00:51:36.559
She doesn’t use Her body for provocating
expressions.

00:51:36.559 --> 00:51:37.559
No.

00:51:37.559 --> 00:51:38.559
She’s a mother.

00:51:38.559 --> 00:51:48.560
So, a lakshmipathi, a man who is supposed
to be adorned by a lakshmi, a rich man, should

00:51:48.560 --> 00:52:04.710
have the personality of a mother, a one who
is lajjasheela as we call it, who is chaste,

00:52:04.710 --> 00:52:16.160
who respects the chastity, who is loving,
generous, affectionate like a mother.

00:52:16.160 --> 00:52:20.799
Mother tolerates all the nonsense of the people,
of the children.

00:52:20.799 --> 00:52:30.840
Then in Her two hands She has two beautiful
pink colored lotuses, two flowers of lotuses.

00:52:30.840 --> 00:52:37.110
The lotus expresses the Shri.

00:52:37.110 --> 00:52:38.470
‘Shri’ means ‘the grace’.

00:52:38.470 --> 00:52:42.890
If I say ‘beauty’, immediately your eyes
will go to those beauty contests.

00:52:42.890 --> 00:52:45.349
I do not mean they are not beautiful.

00:52:45.349 --> 00:52:48.819
‘Beautiful’ is not a word which these
days means ‘provocating’.

00:52:48.819 --> 00:52:49.819
No.

00:52:49.819 --> 00:53:02.250
Beauty means the complete personality that
emits vibrations, which is a form or is the

00:53:02.250 --> 00:53:10.930
same as joy and ananda, that we call ananda,
joy and also consciousness.

00:53:10.930 --> 00:53:14.339
That is a very complicated thing.

00:53:14.339 --> 00:53:23.240
So, I would just say that is the form that
emits the vibrations of joy.

00:53:23.240 --> 00:53:31.410
In Her hands are two lotus flowers which are
pink.

00:53:31.410 --> 00:53:37.920
Means such a person has to be a warm person,
has to be a cozy personality, and his house

00:53:37.920 --> 00:53:39.609
should be as cozy.

00:53:39.609 --> 00:53:43.359
It should not be all polished and varnished.

00:53:43.359 --> 00:53:47.660
And if somebody comes in the house, he drops
anything, flowers there, the woman starts

00:53:47.660 --> 00:53:48.960
getting angry or the man says, “Oh, you
have dirtied my house.

00:53:48.960 --> 00:53:50.910
Will you please clean it."

00:53:50.910 --> 00:53:53.950
Such a house is not a home.

00:53:53.950 --> 00:53:56.630
It has to be a home for all the people.

00:53:56.630 --> 00:53:59.690
Such a man is lakshmipathi.

00:53:59.690 --> 00:54:02.559
Otherwise morning till evening the fighting
going on between husband and wife, “You

00:54:02.559 --> 00:54:03.559
didn’t keep the house clean.

00:54:03.559 --> 00:54:05.089
You must clean this and you must sweep that."

00:54:05.089 --> 00:54:09.680
As if the cleanliness has become the main
part of human life.

00:54:09.680 --> 00:54:11.829
I can understand a basic cleanliness should
be there.

00:54:11.829 --> 00:54:15.581
For Indians we should not tell this because
they lack that completely.

00:54:15.581 --> 00:54:18.490
They are the other extreme, “Raste me chalet
chalet jaha deko thook dhena ka."

00:54:18.490 --> 00:54:20.990
Of course.

00:54:20.990 --> 00:54:26.490
But another extreme also is not good that
all the time the divorces are taking place

00:54:26.490 --> 00:54:33.950
because of cleanliness so fussy that you can’t
live together.

00:54:33.950 --> 00:54:37.780
You develop a sort of a mania or sort of … You
become abnormal people.

00:54:37.780 --> 00:54:41.460
You suffer from the sickness of cleanliness
morning till evening.

00:54:41.460 --> 00:54:44.269
Afraid, “This is to be done, otherwise it
will be dirty."

00:54:44.269 --> 00:54:47.819
You think ten steps forward march that the
place should not be dirty.

00:54:47.819 --> 00:54:50.810
Of course it should not be dirty, is a simple
thing.

00:54:50.810 --> 00:54:55.730
But it should not be that much worked out
that the home becomes a hospital.

00:54:55.730 --> 00:54:57.510
Home is a home.

00:54:57.510 --> 00:55:00.180
Children must feel it’s a home.

00:55:00.180 --> 00:55:02.849
Let them play, let them spoil.

00:55:02.849 --> 00:55:06.430
In London you’ll be surprised my husband’s
secretary told Me that, “My children were

00:55:06.430 --> 00:55:07.710
coming, that aren’t You worried?”

00:55:07.710 --> 00:55:08.710
I said, “Why?”

00:55:08.710 --> 00:55:10.970
She said, “Your house will be all spoiled."

00:55:10.970 --> 00:55:11.970
I said, “What?

00:55:11.970 --> 00:55:16.440
My children are coming, My grand-children
are coming, I’m looking forward for everything

00:55:16.440 --> 00:55:17.609
that I can do for them.

00:55:17.609 --> 00:55:20.260
How did it come into your head that My house
will be spoiled?”

00:55:20.260 --> 00:55:21.260
It can be cleaned.

00:55:21.260 --> 00:55:26.510
You have so many ways of cleaning the house.

00:55:26.510 --> 00:55:28.369
So the house should be cozy and comfortable.

00:55:28.369 --> 00:55:36.070
And such a person who is rich is not a lakshmipathi.

00:55:36.070 --> 00:55:51.010
But a lakshmipathi is a rich person, he receives
people with a big heart.

00:55:51.010 --> 00:56:00.650
So the coziness of the lotus should be in
that lakshmi.

00:56:00.650 --> 00:56:10.400
In another hand, in the two other hands, one
hand has this symbol like this, another is

00:56:10.400 --> 00:56:12.279
like this.

00:56:12.279 --> 00:56:16.839
This suggests that such a man must do “dhan”
[altruism].

00:56:16.839 --> 00:56:21.510
Now, in English I don’t know what is the
word for ‘dhana’ because nothing is that

00:56:21.510 --> 00:56:22.510
dignified.

00:56:22.510 --> 00:56:24.079
‘Dhan’ means ‘giving alms’.

00:56:24.079 --> 00:56:26.970
But it is not dignified word.

00:56:26.970 --> 00:56:35.980
Gavin, what word will you say for ‘dhan’,
tell Me in English?

00:56:35.980 --> 00:56:43.410
‘Charity’ is also little bit, you see,
‘to be charitable’ means you see, you

00:56:43.410 --> 00:56:48.550
are higher than the person whom you charity.

00:56:48.550 --> 00:56:52.190
‘Offering’ if you say then it’s a different
meaning in.

00:56:52.190 --> 00:56:56.450
But, I would say ‘dhan’ means ‘by which
sharing is expressed’, ‘sharing’.

00:56:56.450 --> 00:57:00.640
‘Generosity’, you think it’s nearest.

00:57:00.640 --> 00:57:02.780
All right.

00:57:02.780 --> 00:57:03.849
‘Generosity’.

00:57:03.849 --> 00:57:08.819
But ‘generosity’, you can say at the most
‘generosity’.

00:57:08.819 --> 00:57:12.920
But ‘giving your generosity’ you can say.

00:57:12.920 --> 00:57:26.279
And by this is ashraya, means there should
be people depending on such a person.

00:57:26.279 --> 00:57:35.980
So, you have to be an enlightened person,
so that people should depend on you.

00:57:35.980 --> 00:57:39.619
A rich man has to be a dignified person.

00:57:39.619 --> 00:57:41.170
But normally it is not.

00:57:41.170 --> 00:57:47.800
A rich man first of all he will start dressing
up like a teenager.

00:57:47.800 --> 00:57:50.670
He might be the age of sixty years.

00:57:50.670 --> 00:57:52.880
You find many like that.

00:57:52.880 --> 00:57:58.849
Immediately all his dignity is fallen off,
as soon as [he becomes?].

00:57:58.849 --> 00:58:02.329
Then he must go to races, he must take to
drinks, he must be found on the street, some

00:58:02.329 --> 00:58:08.059
policeman must… and it must appear in the
paper.

00:58:08.059 --> 00:58:15.170
Now, I’ve seen some also horrid things about
women who are rich.

00:58:15.170 --> 00:58:18.369
I must say that this happened in England.

00:58:18.369 --> 00:58:19.369
But it’s funny, for you people it will be
funny, but it’s common there.

00:58:19.369 --> 00:58:26.730
A ninety year old woman, rich woman, ninety
year old rich woman having a love affair with

00:58:26.730 --> 00:58:29.079
a nineteen year old boy.

00:58:29.079 --> 00:58:31.260
She’s a rich woman, you see.

00:58:31.260 --> 00:58:35.750
I mean, I do not know what to call this stupidity.

00:58:35.750 --> 00:58:40.200
They aren’t rich in India, God save.

00:58:40.200 --> 00:58:44.640
No enlightenment of any kind they have.

00:58:44.640 --> 00:58:53.850
If they had there would have been no problems
at all.

00:58:53.850 --> 00:59:01.882
So, this is a symbol of Lakshmi at this stage.

00:59:01.882 --> 00:59:07.500
The sustaining power is the Lakshmi.

00:59:07.500 --> 00:59:11.040
The sustenance, what should be the dharma
and all that.

