Now I find if I discuss it will be too much.

00:59:13.730 --> 00:59:17.849
But I told you for example drinking goes against
the dharma of life.

00:59:17.849 --> 00:59:27.030
It goes against the dharma of man because
it goes against the awareness of man.

00:59:27.030 --> 00:59:31.750
If you loose your awareness how are you going
to rise to a higher awareness?

00:59:31.750 --> 00:59:39.220
Now, people know by drinking these things
happen but they will say, “What does it

00:59:39.220 --> 00:59:43.210
matter, Mataji, if we drink a little bit for
our society?”

00:59:43.210 --> 00:59:48.400
And what does it matter if I take a little
poison?

00:59:48.400 --> 00:59:50.369
You’ll get used to it.

00:59:50.369 --> 00:59:53.200
Gradually you’ll start taking poison.

00:59:53.200 --> 00:59:59.790
There are so many people, in this country
specially, if they take a little of tobacco

00:59:59.790 --> 01:00:03.960
they feel giddy and fall on the ground, this
tobacco.

01:00:03.960 --> 01:00:05.640
There must be some in you also.

01:00:05.640 --> 01:00:07.109
They cannot even look at tobacco.

01:00:07.109 --> 01:00:08.109
There must be some.

01:00:08.109 --> 01:00:14.920
But there are some who can take tons, tons
inside their being.

01:00:14.920 --> 01:00:16.529
How is it?

01:00:16.529 --> 01:00:19.579
Both are human beings.

01:00:19.579 --> 01:00:27.119
So, by little and little, those countries
who have accepted this as a social thing have

01:00:27.119 --> 01:00:28.119
done the greatest harm to themselves.

01:00:28.119 --> 01:00:32.740
Because in the beginning they were taking
only little, little.

01:00:32.740 --> 01:00:35.349
That was I should say about 100 years back,
you can say about 200 years back.

01:00:35.349 --> 01:00:38.859
But today if you go and see them, they are
alcoholic.

01:00:38.859 --> 01:00:41.000
They can’t live without.

01:00:41.000 --> 01:00:56.599
So the pioneers were the little ones and the
sufferers are those now who are fed up with

01:00:56.599 --> 01:00:57.599
alcohols.

