Because they think it doesn’t mean intoxicate,
so they have taken to drugs also.

01:01:01.300 --> 01:01:06.710
And they think it is another experiment.

01:01:06.710 --> 01:01:13.910
So you have more police force, you do all
kinds of things to control it.

01:01:13.910 --> 01:01:15.220
It’s not possible.

01:01:15.220 --> 01:01:21.480
Mohamed Sahib has clearly said, “No intoxications.

01:01:21.480 --> 01:01:25.059
Nothing, nothing at all."

01:01:25.059 --> 01:01:29.539
Nanak has said the same.

01:01:29.539 --> 01:01:32.470
They are both the same people you’ll be
surprised.

01:01:32.470 --> 01:01:37.180
Same people born at different times, same
people teaching the same thing.

01:01:37.180 --> 01:01:42.880
Nanak said the same thing, “No smoking,
nothing."

01:01:42.880 --> 01:01:46.359
But today there are no Sikhs.

01:01:46.359 --> 01:01:50.349
In the morning they were, Sikhs are fighting
in London that, “We should not wear the

01:01:50.349 --> 01:01:51.349
helmet."

01:01:51.349 --> 01:01:52.349
Imagine.

01:01:52.349 --> 01:01:53.349
Where is it written?

01:01:53.349 --> 01:01:58.329
In which book Nanak Sahib has written this,
“I would like to see, that helmet."

01:01:58.329 --> 01:02:01.720
On the contrary He said, “Vesh ka kya payda
ka”, “What is the use of changing your

01:02:01.720 --> 01:02:02.720
dress?”

01:02:02.720 --> 01:02:04.861
And they are fighting on this point.

01:02:04.861 --> 01:02:10.670
But the way the Sikhs drink in London, I mean
the British are ashamed.

01:02:10.670 --> 01:02:22.609
I mean they think they are no good compared
to Sikhs, the way they can consume.

01:02:22.609 --> 01:02:24.220
And they are fighting in the name of religion.

01:02:24.220 --> 01:02:31.410
Is a fact I’m telling you that the helmet
they cannot wear because they must have a

01:02:31.410 --> 01:02:37.220
right and freedom to crack their heads on
a scooter.

01:02:37.220 --> 01:02:38.220
What is this?

01:02:38.220 --> 01:02:48.160
And there is a big procession every, I think
every Sunday they take it out “against protecting."

01:02:48.160 --> 01:02:51.470
My head off to all these people.

01:02:51.470 --> 01:02:52.900
That is what they have done out of Nanak Sahib.

01:02:52.900 --> 01:02:57.589
And the Muslims, think of them, they have
written poetry on drinking.

01:02:57.589 --> 01:03:06.359
Now, if I say you don’t have to drink, they
will think this lady is talking some of about

01:03:06.359 --> 01:03:07.460
ten thousand years back.

01:03:07.460 --> 01:03:14.960
But is a fact I’m telling you, it is not
meant for human consumption at all, none of

01:03:14.960 --> 01:03:15.960
these.

01:03:15.960 --> 01:03:19.839
Now they might say that Christ was drinking
wine.

01:03:19.839 --> 01:03:23.920
Now, ‘wine’ never means ‘alcohol’.

01:03:23.920 --> 01:03:28.160
I mean grape juice which is fresh, which is
unfermented is different.

01:03:28.160 --> 01:03:36.519
But the fermented, even molasses, anything
you can ferment, it becomes an alcohol, which

01:03:36.519 --> 01:03:37.519
is satanic.

01:03:37.519 --> 01:03:44.240
Is a process only to be used for polishing
things.

01:03:44.240 --> 01:03:53.029
You are drinking the polish and all your intestines
all are polished off nicely.

01:03:53.029 --> 01:03:56.920
And your liver is ruined.

01:03:56.920 --> 01:03:59.289
And then you come to Mataji, “Mataji, our
liver is ruined.

01:03:59.289 --> 01:04:00.289
Now what to do?

01:04:00.289 --> 01:04:02.190
How to cure it?”

01:04:02.190 --> 01:04:05.799
Now, if I tell you, “Don’t drink.

01:04:05.799 --> 01:04:06.810
It’s very bad."

01:04:06.810 --> 01:04:09.880
But these days there are gurus like that you
know, they say, “You drink.

01:04:09.880 --> 01:04:11.309
Do whatever you like.

01:04:11.309 --> 01:04:14.890
Only thing, give your purse please behind
me.

01:04:14.890 --> 01:04:17.070
You can do whatever thing, can even smuggle”,
you see.

01:04:17.070 --> 01:04:19.450
There was a guru who was teaching smuggling,
actually smuggling to people.

01:04:19.450 --> 01:04:22.960
And all the Sehasas [Sikhs] were caught in
Jakarta when they were smuggling.

01:04:22.960 --> 01:04:25.799
They lost billions and billions of dollars
there.

01:04:25.799 --> 01:04:28.650
And when I went to Singapore they came to
Me, “This has happened."

01:04:28.650 --> 01:04:31.100
I said, “Now where is your guru?”

01:04:31.100 --> 01:04:32.859
“She has gone to Switzerland."

01:04:32.859 --> 01:04:33.859
I said, “Very nice."

01:04:33.859 --> 01:04:34.859
He said, “You do whatever you like.

01:04:34.859 --> 01:04:35.859
Bring the purse here, that’s all.

01:04:35.859 --> 01:04:37.779
If you cannot look after your wife and children
leave them here also.

01:04:37.779 --> 01:04:43.390
You sacrifice everything in the name of God
and give everything to me, very nicely.

01:04:43.390 --> 01:04:44.619
