01:25:03.130 --> 01:25:04.330
What is a diplomat?

01:25:04.330 --> 01:25:14.080
Diplomat is a person who is a sakshi, who
is a witness who plays the divine diplomacy.

01:25:14.080 --> 01:25:19.780
He played the divine diplomacy, and you are
still in that diplomacy when you read Gita,

01:25:19.780 --> 01:25:21.340
very much.

01:25:21.340 --> 01:25:26.160
I’ll tell you in two sentences how to understand
His diplomacy in Gita, very necessary.

01:25:26.160 --> 01:25:38.610
He said in the very beginning, at the very
outset that you seek in within yourself.

01:25:38.610 --> 01:25:41.410
He told Arjuna, “You seek in within yourself.

01:25:41.410 --> 01:25:42.740
You have to become a sakshi."

01:25:42.740 --> 01:25:50.330
Arjuna being a mediocre, asked Him a question
that, “You are saying that, ‘You must

01:25:50.330 --> 01:25:53.990
seek in within yourself, you should become
a sakshi, a witness’ and here you are telling

01:25:53.990 --> 01:26:02.350
me to go on the war, to kill people, kill
my own brothers, kill my own relation!”

01:26:02.350 --> 01:26:03.910
What He wanted to say that it’s all a play.

01:26:03.910 --> 01:26:07.560
But it only becomes a play when you become
that witness, when you are Realized.

01:26:07.560 --> 01:26:10.350
That’s what He told him.

01:26:10.350 --> 01:26:14.810
But Arjuna was a mediocre in this respect.

01:26:14.810 --> 01:26:22.520
So He being a Father, He understood.

01:26:22.520 --> 01:26:28.040
Like a father who comes out of his hut and
see his son beating the cart, so he tells

01:26:28.040 --> 01:26:33.590
him, “You bring the horse in front of the
cart then only the cart will going to move

01:26:33.590 --> 01:26:34.590
on."

01:26:34.590 --> 01:26:36.980
But the child, the son, doesn’t want to
listen to his father.

01:26:36.980 --> 01:26:39.550
He says, “No, I am going to beat the cart."

01:26:39.550 --> 01:26:43.890
So, He plays the diplomacy, the Father.

01:26:43.890 --> 01:26:44.890
The Mother does not.

01:26:44.890 --> 01:26:45.890
Mother tells you the fact.

01:26:45.890 --> 01:26:49.980
So, He played the diplomacy there, divine
diplomacy.

01:26:49.980 --> 01:26:57.680
He says, “All right you go on beating but
keep your attention on the horse and you will

01:26:57.680 --> 01:26:58.680
go forward."

01:26:58.680 --> 01:27:01.520
That’s an absurd, absurd thing.

01:27:01.520 --> 01:27:04.720
It cannot happen, you know.

01:27:04.720 --> 01:27:06.530
He told something absurd.

01:27:06.530 --> 01:27:12.550
So, He says, “All right, do your karmas
but put it at the feet of the Lord."

01:27:12.550 --> 01:27:13.560
You cannot do it.

01:27:13.560 --> 01:27:14.560
It cannot be done.

01:27:14.560 --> 01:27:18.250
This is something an impossibility because
there is the ego in you.

01:27:18.250 --> 01:27:21.930
If you do any work and if you think, “Oh,
I’m putting everything at the feet of the

01:27:21.930 --> 01:27:23.600
Lord,” you are just deceiving yourself.

01:27:23.600 --> 01:27:24.970
This is His diplomacy He played it here.

01:27:24.970 --> 01:27:25.970
You cannot.

01:27:25.970 --> 01:27:31.170
Those who believe in such a thing should know
that it’s a deception.

01:27:31.170 --> 01:27:34.370
It can only happen when you become a hollow
personality.

01:27:34.370 --> 01:27:37.770
For these people now, those who are Realized,
you will see them saying, “It’s going,

01:27:37.770 --> 01:27:38.770
it’s coming."

01:27:38.770 --> 01:27:42.420
They do not say that, “I’m giving, I’m
doing."

01:27:42.420 --> 01:27:46.820
You have to become a hollow thing like this
which just stands and sees and passes through

01:27:46.820 --> 01:27:47.820
it.

01:27:47.820 --> 01:27:49.460
The Divine has to flow through you.

01:27:49.460 --> 01:27:53.420
