is another diplomacy.

01:27:53.420 --> 01:27:58.160
You see, His words, you see, nobody sees I’m
surprised.

01:27:58.160 --> 01:28:01.300
They have written five hundred books on Gita.

01:28:01.300 --> 01:28:04.442
