01:29:53.800 --> 01:29:59.500
Now how do you know a person is a Realized
bhakti or not?

01:29:59.500 --> 01:30:00.500
Very easy.

01:30:00.500 --> 01:30:07.290
A person who speaks of separation, like Surdas,
he was not a Realized soul.

01:30:07.290 --> 01:30:12.160
Those who talk of their tortures, “Oh, God,
