01:30:12.160 --> 01:30:15.390
they are not realized souls.

01:30:15.390 --> 01:30:20.570
But those like Kabir and Nanak, like Christ.

01:30:20.570 --> 01:30:23.160
Christ was an incarnation.

01:30:23.160 --> 01:30:30.380
But those who talk and sing the praise of
meeting are the people who are realized.

01:30:30.380 --> 01:30:35.550
I mean a person who has met God why should
he talk of separation?

01:30:35.550 --> 01:30:36.740
Very simple thing.

01:30:36.740 --> 01:30:45.000
But we like the songs of the people who talk
of their – you see, I don’t know what

01:30:45.000 --> 01:30:49.430
